Installation
============

From PyPI
------------

    pip3 install pomodorotimer --user

From sources
------------

Alternatively you can install **pomodorotimer** from sources directory:

    git clone https://github.com/patsuckow/pomodorotimer
    cd pomodorotimer
    pip3 install -r requirements.txt
    pip3 install . --user
    cd ..
    rm -rf pomodorotimer
